Life Begins Again is the debut album by the Jimmy Chamberlin Complex (side project band of The Smashing Pumpkins/Zwan drummer Jimmy Chamberlin). It was released on January 25, 2005. The album stars several guest musicians and vocalists including Billy Corgan (Smashing Pumpkins) on Loki Cat, Bill Medley (The Righteous Brothers) on Lullabye, and Rob Dickinson (Catherine Wheel) on Life Begins Again and Love Is Real.
